text: Michael Murphy (12 June 1854 - 2 September 1890) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class cricket match for Victoria in 1874. ==See also== * List of Victoria first-class cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1854 births Category:1890 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:Victoria cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney Category:Melbourne Cricket Club cricketers
